OL,4,CTesco staff win legal argument in equal
OL,5,Cpay fight
OL,6, Thousands of current and former Tesco
OL,7, workers have won a legal argument in
OL,8, their fight for equal pay.
OL,10,FThe European Court of Justice has ruled
OL,11,Fthat an EU law could be relied on in
OL,12,Fmaking equal pay claims against their
OL,13,Femployer.
OL,15,FTesco workers, mostly women, have
OL,16,Fargued that they failed to receive
OL,17,Fequal pay for work of equal value with
OL,18,Fcolleagues in its distribution centres
OL,19,Fwho are mostly men.
OL,21,FThey said this breached EU and UK laws.
